Package: cat.vader
Title: Social Media Content Classification with LLMs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Chris", "Soria", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "chris.soria@nyu.edu")
Description: R interface to the Python catvader package. Classifies, extracts,
    and explores social media content using LLMs. A thin domain wrapper around
    cat.stack that adds social media sourcing parameters (platform, handle,
    hashtags, credentials).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
